Although the [$watermelon#Plant*] isolate is serologically related to the [@groundnut bud necrosis virus#Virus*] ([@GBNV#Virus*]) from India, it differs in host range.
This is the first report of [$tospovirus#Virus*] naturally infecting [$watermelon#Plant*] in India.